<br>
That being said, if avatar isn't currently active when it is time to engage a major beastie as MT, many tanks ask a friendly primal avatar enabled shammy for avatar buff on inc, so they don't need to bother swapping in their primal and waiting for the proc before switching to their aggro-matic 2000 super weapons.<br>
<br>
Avatar lasts six minutes, so it's generally not a lot of trouble to swap it in until it procs then replace it with your other weapons.  As long as I catch it before I lose the 100 dex, I usually get a proc within 15-30 seconds with my 2 hander.... and then I am good for another 5 and a half minutes :)<br>
<br>
Having a primal bow is great for a range slot stat item and it eliminates the need for swapping stat items when pulling and tagging, but I wouldn't want to have to swap to a bow in order to get my avatar fix :)<br>
