r me unbuffed.  thats comparing priceless to primal, so the weapons were all 13/20 <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=7023  target="web">smushums<a</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uthedrunkenmage.showPublicProfile?language=EN>The Drunken Mage</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 80<br> <font color=#FF0000>(9/17/02 10:38:11 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3902.topic&index=10>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_ale.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: primal question</span><hr size=1> Getting off the topic a bit, but since it came up...<br>
<br>
I parsed my shadowheart/priceless combo both with and without avatar, using the soulbinder before they changed them.<br>
<br>
